{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-doc-page-js","path":"/goals/platforms/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"work-in-progress-notes\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#work-in-progress-notes\" aria-label=\"work in progress notes permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>WORK IN PROGRESS NOTES</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Synthesize the product function</li>\n<li>Justifying funding for the platform team can be difficult as it is indirect business value</li>\n<li>AuxEng allows you to staff a platform team up with senior talent while still directly contributing to business outcomes</li>\n<li>Knowing the right problems to solve can be difficult. Being embedded brings challenges, low hanging fruit to the surface.\n<ul>\n<li>Impossible for a senior engineer to know what it’s like to be a junior engineer, or not know the platform</li>\n<li>Seeing a junior engineer struggle makes points of friction clear</li>\n<li>Engineers experiencing pain don’t always realize when something is easy to improve.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Giving AuxEngineers 1 day per week to make self-directed investments / explorations in the platform gives them is powerful\n<ul>\n<li>Self-direction is powerful. Process adds friction</li>\n<li>Short feedback loops. Experience pain -> Solve problem</li>\n<li>Writing documentation can be draining, but not nearly as much when you are solving a problem just experienced first hand\n<ul>\n<li>You feel like you’re helping someone</li>\n<li>That person validates and expresses gratitude. Feels rewarding</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/goals/platforms/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Platform","image":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/fcb4df312ea3e87a9d57ffaf89a97635/87cb2/goals.png","height":400,"width":600}}}}},"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"1bb25e95-0500-5f3d-a7ac-5d70a79b5ac6","fields":{"slug":"/example/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Example Engagement"},"parent":{"relativeDirectory":""}}},{"node":{"id":"d7cb5ed0-023c-5852-87d8-bd7e31539240","fields":{"slug":"/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Auxiliary Engineering"},"parent":{"relativeDirectory":""}}},{"node":{"id":"17cc72ec-d11b-5495-89fc-75c95b7a87e6","fields":{"slug":"/goals/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Engagement Goals"},"parent":{"relativeDirectory":""}}},{"node":{"id":"fdd89c5b-6e0a-510a-ae71-efa493c1de19","fields":{"slug":"/running/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Running Engagements"},"parent":{"relativeDirectory":""}}},{"node":{"id":"7dfa138a-69b5-5523-8af4-7899829e39e8","fields":{"slug":"/theory/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Theory"},"parent":{"relativeDirectory":""}}},{"node":{"id":"9686b18f-d63e-5aba-8615-bfe284dd9534","fields":{"slug":"/example/overview/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Work In Progress Notes"},"parent":{"relativeDirectory":"example"}}},{"node":{"id":"01e6394f-bb9b-5550-90c2-37cfd7440444","fields":{"slug":"/goals/careers/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Career"},"parent":{"relativeDirectory":"goals"}}},{"node":{"id":"1c6b36ec-585d-5011-b21a-ff43147f317e","fields":{"slug":"/goals/mobility/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Mobility"},"parent":{"relativeDirectory":"goals"}}},{"node":{"id":"28cdaf51-d9d8-51fa-ba1e-5e52baf5bf11","fields":{"slug":"/goals/diffusion/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Organizational"},"parent":{"relativeDirectory":"goals"}}},{"node":{"id":"d00fe56b-e02a-5fe3-b827-b4622f092036","fields":{"slug":"/goals/platforms/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Platform"},"parent":{"relativeDirectory":"goals"}}},{"node":{"id":"45aa